KAZUO NITTA, Appellant, v. Edward L. HAFF, District Director of Immigration for the Port of San Francisco, California, Appel-lee. No. 7589. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 20, 1935.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon consideration of the stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
